vote.title: An ordinance granting a private license to Mt. Pentelicus Devco, LLC for the use of a total of approximately 1,653 square feet of land to occupy, maintain and utilize three subsurface conduits, thirty-four bollards and eleven light poles on and under portions of Akard, Elm and Field Streets rights-of-way located near the intersection with Akard and Elm Streets - Revenue: General Fund $3,865.00 annually and $400.00 one-time fee, plus the $20.00 ordinance publication fee
